players against common foes. In multiplayer FPS titles, teams of players will come together
and face one another until there is only one player left standing.</p>
<h3 style="margin-left:40px;">Strategy</h3>
  <p>These titles capitalize on strategic elements in order to accomplish the primary objective.
  Many well-known strategy games include building cities, civilizations, and even simulated businesses.
Other strategy games are simulated versions of classic table-top board games, such as chess.</p>
